			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This is for the edgecase in which one of the parents has died. In this case - Locke, the husband survives. In the first scenarion he rewards and thanks the player for saving his daughter's life - lamenting briefly on their lives without Arabella's mother.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;In the second, he learns that Arabella has died. He is overcome with grief and rage at losing both his wife and daughter. " />
